This package contains a Hematite-maintained fork of code derived from:

  lucasjinreal/Kokoros
  https://github.com/lucasjinreal/Kokoros

Upstream README copyright note:

  "Copyright reserved by Lucas Jin under Apache License."

Hematite-specific modifications include:

- removing upstream C++/system dependency assumptions from the vendored fork
- aligning ONNX Runtime setup with Hematite's local Windows packaging flow
- packaging the fork under the distinct crates.io package name `hematite-kokoros`
  while preserving the Rust library crate path `kokoros`
